702911f-b.title: Brooklyn: 92nd Street (East) - Avenue J
702911f-b.text:
East 92nd Street, west side, between Avenues J and E,
showing the Grace Methodist Episcopal Church. The church was
located at the S. W. correr of the road that led to the old Lott
House, before it was abandoned.
July 6, 1933
Views 1,2
P. L. Sperr

702912f-b.title: Brooklyn: 92nd Street (East) - Avenue J
702912f-b.text:
East 92nd Street, west side, between Avenues J and K,
showing the Grace Methodist Episcopal Church. The view is east
along the old road that led to the Lott House, the church being
located at the S. W. corner of this road and East 92nd Stroet,
before the former was abandoned.
View 1: January, 1928
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection
VViews 2,3
July e, 1933
P. L. Sperr
